#: ../../source/janim/items/geometry/polygon.rst:2
msgid "polygon"
msgstr "polygon"

#: janim.items.geometry.polygon.Polygon:1 of
msgid "多边形"
msgstr "Polygon"

#: ../../source/janim/items/geometry/polygon.rst
msgid "参数"
msgstr "Parameters"

#: janim.items.geometry.polygon.Polygon:3 of
msgid "顶点序列，按顺序连接构成多边形"
msgstr "A sequence of vertices connected in order to form a polygon"

#: janim.items.geometry.polygon.Polygon:4 of
msgid "是否将最后一个顶点与第一个顶点闭合连接，默认为 ``True`` 闭合"
msgstr "Whether to close the path by connecting the last vertex to the first; default is ``True`` (closed)"

#: janim.items.geometry.polygon.Polygon.reshape:1 janim.items.geometry.polygon.Rect.reshape:1
#: janim.items.geometry.polygon.RegularPolygon.reshape:1 janim.items.geometry.polygon.RoundedRect.reshape:1
#: janim.items.geometry.polygon.Square.reshape:1 janim.items.geometry.polygon.Star.reshape:1 of
msgid "类似传递给 ``__init__`` 的参数，重新设置几何物件的形状"
msgstr "Similar to passing parameters to ``__init__``, reset the shape of the geometry item"

#: janim.items.geometry.polygon.Polygon.reshape:3 janim.items.geometry.polygon.Rect.reshape:3
#: janim.items.geometry.polygon.RegularPolygon.reshape:3 janim.items.geometry.polygon.RoundedRect.reshape:3
#: janim.items.geometry.polygon.Square.reshape:3 janim.items.geometry.polygon.Star.reshape:3 of
msgid "可以缺省部分值，表示使用先前的；具体用法请参考 :ref:`geometry_reshape` 文档教程"
msgstr ""
"Some values can be omitted to reuse previous ones; for detailed usage, refer to the :ref:`geometry_reshape` tutorial"

#: janim.items.geometry.polygon.Polyline:1 of
msgid "多边形折线"
msgstr "Polyline"

#: janim.items.geometry.polygon.Polyline:3 of
msgid "折线顶点序列，按顺序连接"
msgstr "A sequence of polyline vertices connected in order"

#: janim.items.geometry.polygon.Polyline:4 of
msgid "是否闭合路径，默认不闭合"
msgstr "Whether to close the path; default is not closed"

#: janim.items.geometry.polygon.RegularPolygon:1 of
msgid "正多边形"
msgstr "Regular polygon"

#: janim.items.geometry.polygon.RegularPolygon:3 of
msgid "边数"
msgstr "Number of sides"

#: janim.items.geometry.polygon.RegularPolygon:4 of
msgid "外接圆半径"
msgstr "Circumradius"

#: janim.items.geometry.polygon.RegularPolygon:5 of
msgid "起始角度；为 ``None`` 时根据边数自动设置"
msgstr "Starting angle; when ``None``, it is set automatically based on the number of sides"

#: janim.items.geometry.polygon.RegularPolygon:7 of
msgid "可通过 ``.mark.get()`` 得到多边形中心"
msgstr "Can get the center of the polygon via ``.mark.get()``"

#: janim.items.geometry.polygon.Triangle:1 of
msgid "正三角形"
msgstr "Equilateral triangle"

#: janim.items.geometry.polygon.Triangle:3 of
msgid "其它参数，另见 :class:`RegularPolygon`"
msgstr "Other parameters, see also :class:`RegularPolygon`"

#: janim.items.geometry.polygon.Rect:1 of
msgid "矩形"
msgstr "Rectangle"

#: janim.items.geometry.polygon.Rect:3 of
msgid "支持两种构建方式：``Rect(width, height)`` 或 ``Rect(corner1, corner2)``"
msgstr "Supports two construction forms: ``Rect(width, height)`` or ``Rect(corner1, corner2)``"

#: janim.items.geometry.polygon.Rect of
msgid "param"
msgstr "param"

#: janim.items.geometry.polygon.Rect:5 janim.items.geometry.polygon.RoundedRect:3 of
msgid "可传入宽高 ``(width, height)``，或传入一对对角顶点 ``(corner1, corner2)``"
msgstr "You can pass width and height ``(width, height)``, or a pair of diagonal corners ``(corner1, corner2)``"

#: janim.items.geometry.polygon.Rect:6 janim.items.geometry.polygon.RoundedRect:5 of
msgid "传递给父类的其它参数"
msgstr "Other parameters passed to the parent class"

#: ../../docstring janim.items.geometry.polygon.Rect.preset_highlight_stroke:1 of
msgid "高亮描边预设（黄色描边），例："
msgstr "Highlight stroke preset (yellow stroke), e.g.:"

#: ../../docstring janim.items.geometry.polygon.Rect.preset_highlight_stroke:3 of
msgid "Rect(p1, p2, **Rect.preset_highlight_stroke)"
msgstr "Rect(p1, p2, **Rect.preset_highlight_stroke)"

#: ../../docstring janim.items.geometry.polygon.Rect.preset_highlight_fill:1 of
msgid "高亮填充预设（半透明黄色填充），例："
msgstr "Highlight fill preset (semi-transparent yellow fill), e.g.:"

#: ../../docstring janim.items.geometry.polygon.Rect.preset_highlight_fill:3 of
msgid "SurroundingRect(item, depth=1, **Rect.preset_highlight_fill)"
msgstr "SurroundingRect(item, depth=1, **Rect.preset_highlight_fill)"

#: ../../docstring janim.items.geometry.polygon.Rect.preset_shadow:1 of
msgid "阴影预设（半透明黑色填充），例："
msgstr "Shadow preset (semi-transparent black fill), e.g.:"

#: ../../docstring janim.items.geometry.polygon.Rect.preset_shadow:3 of
msgid "SurroundingRect(item, depth=1, **Rect.preset_shadow)"
msgstr "SurroundingRect(item, depth=1, **Rect.preset_shadow)"

#: janim.items.geometry.polygon.Square:1 of
msgid "正方形"
msgstr "Square"

#: janim.items.geometry.polygon.Square:3 of
msgid "正方形边长"
msgstr "Side length of the square"

#: janim.items.geometry.polygon.RoundedRect:1 of
msgid "圆角矩形"
msgstr "Rounded rectangle"

#: janim.items.geometry.polygon.RoundedRect:4 of
msgid "圆角半径"
msgstr "Corner radius"

#: janim.items.geometry.polygon.Star:1 of
msgid "星形"
msgstr "Star"

#: janim.items.geometry.polygon.Star:3 of
msgid "顶点数，默认为 5"
msgstr "Number of vertices, default is 5"

#: janim.items.geometry.polygon.Star:4 of
msgid "外半径"
msgstr "Outer radius"

#: janim.items.geometry.polygon.Star:5 of
msgid "内半径；为 ``None`` 时由 ``density`` 计算"
msgstr "Inner radius; when ``None``, it is computed from ``density``"

#: janim.items.geometry.polygon.Star:6 of
msgid ""
"密度，数值越高内半径越小，取值范围 ``[1, n/2]``；含义可理解为一笔画时的“每个连线之间跳过多少个顶点”，默认每次跳过一个顶点"
"即连成星形"
msgstr ""
"Density. Larger values produce a smaller inner radius. Valid range is ``[1, n/2]``; it can be understood as \"how many "
"vertices to skip between each connected segment\" when drawing in one stroke. By default, one vertex is skipped each time "
"to form a star"

#: janim.items.geometry.polygon.Star:7 of
msgid "起始角度"
msgstr "Starting angle"

#: janim.items.geometry.polygon.Star.inner_radius_of_density:1 of
msgid "计算指定 ``density`` 下，``outer_radius`` 所对应的 ``inner_radius``"
msgstr "Compute the ``inner_radius`` corresponding to ``outer_radius`` under the specified ``density``"

#~ msgid "传入顶点列表 ``verts`` 进行表示"
#~ msgstr "Pass a vertex list ``verts`` for representation"

#~ msgid "与 :class:`Polygon` 的区别是，不会自动将最后一个点与第一个点连接"
#~ msgstr "The difference from :class:`Polygon` is that it does not automatically connect the last point to the first point"

#~ msgid "传入数字 ``n`` 表示边数"
#~ msgstr "Pass a number ``n`` to represent the number of sides"

#~ msgid "可以使用 ``Rect(4, 2)`` 的传入宽高的方式进行构建"
#~ msgstr "Can be constructed by passing width and height like ``Rect(4, 2)``"

#~ msgid "也可以使用 ``Rect(p1, p2)`` 的传入对角顶点的方式进行构建"
#~ msgstr "Can also be constructed by passing diagonal vertices like ``Rect(p1, p2)``"

#~ msgid "``side_length`` 表示正方形边长"
#~ msgstr "``side_length`` represents the side length of the square"

#~ msgid "``outer_radius`` 表示外半径"
#~ msgstr "``outer_radius`` represents the outer radius"

#~ msgid "``density`` 表示密度，数值越高，内半径越小，取值范围 ``[1, n/2]``"
#~ msgstr "``density`` represents density, higher values mean smaller inner radius, value range is ``[1, n/2]``"

#~ msgid "``start_angle`` 表示起始角度，即星形的旋转角度"
#~ msgstr "``start_angle`` represents the starting angle, i.e., the rotation angle of the star"
